| Tasks | <%= systemMetrics && systemMetrics.tasksDone %> / <%= systemMetrics && systemMetrics.tasksTotal %> (<%= systemMetrics && systemMetrics.completionRate %>% done) |
| Open questions | <%= systemMetrics && systemMetrics.openQuestionsCount %> |
